Dialogs.Dialog: See, now that we're here, you know what I mean, right？
I can't help it... I want to do it now.
Do you just not get it？ Or is that on purpose？
Was it not good enough now？
Is it okay to wait for it？
That's what this is all about, right？
I told you it's still no good.
Do you want me to come to you？
Hmm？ You called me, didn't you？
You don't have to be so withdrawn.
You sound like a man now.
Hehe, being pushy is good sometimes.
I really, really wanted to make up with you as soon as possible.
Look at that！ ...Oh, I guess I was imagining it.
Well, don't get me started on that.
Be nice to me or I'll get mad, okay？
You know, Rinko... Nah, it's nothing.
I feel like I'm in a dream.
Rather than being shy... I'm happy.
It's a world just for us, right？
I don't want anyone to get in my way...
I'm going to have you all to myself the whole time！
I wonder what this feeling is.
Say you love me a lot more.
I won't say I don't like it.
I don't know which one of us is more spoiled...
It's like my body is floating.
Will you take good care of Rinko？
You're looking at me too much.
My body temperature may be rising...
That's all we've been doing since a while ago...
Hey, there are other places, too...
You keep going for the same place... it's weird.
Hiya！ My voice has gone inside out.
My head is starting to spin...
Hmm！ I let my voice out...
Are you in kissing mode now？
You don't have to be so pushy...
You... Hah, I can't help it.
You keep focusing on my ears.
Don't keep me waiting too long, okay？
I'm liking it more and more...
It's you, so it must be good.
Hmmm... I was a little surprised.
Geez... are you trying to be mean？
You know, Rinko will kiss you.
Hehe... You know what Rinko wants to do？
Hey... did we get close again？
Again... I feel more fond of you.
Nope. I prefer a different place.
Hehe... I was mean to you.
There's more to it than that, isn't there？
If you think this is the end, you're wrong♪
Don't stop... can you kiss me more？
I want to keep kissing you like this all the time...
How far do you want to go？
Are you okay with all this kissing？ Rinko is...
My senses have gone crazy in many ways.
Is there any greater happiness than this？
The word "I love you" is not enough...
You and Rinko love each other.
You're the only one I can see...
I'd like to do it again.
I can't think of anything more...
Whew... Is it okay to be so happy？
I can't live without you anymore.
You're responsible for making Rinko love you so much, aren't you？
Rinko is already thinking about our next kiss...
You can tell by her face, right？ Rinko is happy.
Your kisses have warmed my heart.
Are you perhaps obsessed with kissing？
Now a lot more... Nah, it's nothing.
Rinko is not a good kisser.
How about a hotter kiss this time？ Hehe.
I can't be mad at you if you kiss me like this.
Rinko was worried about you... Hehe.
It's not like I dislike it...
Don't be too hard on me.
Hah, I'm so happy with this...
That's out of the blue... It's okay...
If it's always like this, it may be a problem.
Geez, my face is so hot...
Just because I don't say no.
